LIBRARY DIBAPI
 
DESCRIPTION  'DIB and Bitmap API sample DLL'
EXETYPE  WINDOWS

SEGMENTS
    WEPSEG      PRELOAD FIXED
    HOOKSEG     PRELOAD FIXED ;Segment with our KeyboardHook proc in it

CODE    PRELOAD MOVEABLE DISCARDABLE
DATA    PRELOAD MOVEABLE SINGLE

HEAPSIZE 8192

EXPORTS
   WEP                      @1     RESIDENTNAME
   _BitmapToDIB             @2
   _ChangeBitmapFormat      @3
   _ChangeDIBFormat         @4
   _CopyScreenToBitmap      @5
   _CopyScreentoDIB         @6
   _CopyWindowToBitmap      @7
   _CopyWindowToDIB         @8
   _CreateDIBPalette        @9
   _CreateDIB               @31
   _DestroyDIB              @10
   _DIBError                @11
   _DIBHeight               @12
   _DIBNumColors            @13
   _DIBToBitmap             @14
   _DIBWidth                @15
   _FindDIBBits             @16
   _GetSystemPalette        @17
   _LoadDIB                 @18
   _PaintBitmap             @19
   _PaintDIB                @20
   _PalEntriesOnDevice      @21
   _PaletteSize             @22
   _PrintDIB                @23
   _PrintScreen             @24
   _PrintWindow             @25
   _SaveDIB                 @26
   PrintAbortDlg            @27
   PrintAbortProc           @28
   InstallHook              @29    ; For Keyboard Hook
   KeyboardHook             @30    ; For Keyboard Hook


    
